abstract: USSR reply to Brit guarantees against re-export of Brit Empire goods to Germany; rejects rationing of other USSR exports or re-exports; reaction in Berlin
snippet: LONDON, April 30 (AP)--British efforts to plug the trade routes to Germany through Russia today met firm Soviet objections to a proposed rationing system....

headline.main: TRADE RATIONING IDEA REJECTED BY RUSSIA; Better Relations With Britain, However, Not Impossible

lead_paragraph: LONDON, April 30 (AP)--British efforts to plug the trade routes to Germany through Russia today met firm Soviet objections to a proposed rationing system.
